elements.name: User login to SMT application and navigate to Store Data tab

steps.name: User is on home page of SMT application
User is able to see login button on home page
User click on login button
User click on Proceed To Login button in "English"
User login as "Store Operator"
User click on "Apply" button
User click on "Programme Data" tab
User wait for "2" seconds

elements.name: Verify user is able to add Routine Vaccine

steps.name: User click on "Add Routine Vaccine" button for "Programme Data"
"Add new routine vaccination" heading is visible
User select "bOPV" from "Vaccine Name" in "Programme Data" tab
User select "Sinovac Life Sciences Co. Ltd." from "Producer" in "Programme Data" tab
User select "Liquid: ready to use" from "Formulation" in "Programme Data" tab
User enter "10" in "dosesTarget"
User select "Adolescent Girls" from "Target Groups" in "Programme Data" tab
User enter "80" in "coverageExpected"
User select "20" from "Presentation" in "Programme Data" tab
User enter "10" in "wastageRates"
User select "ADS_0.05ml" from "Administration Type" in "Programme Data" tab
User select "ADS_0.1ml" from "Dilution-Syringes" in "Programme Data" tab
User click on "Save" button
Routine Vaccine Data is created successfully
User wait for "10" seconds
Routine Vaccine producer "Sinovac Life Sciences Co. Ltd." is visible in Routine Vaccination table to user
